Hi, Iâ€™m Alex Paul, Im a latin artist, musician, producer and audiovisual designer from one of the northernmost cities on the Tamaulipas-Texas border in the Mexican side; Nuevo Laredo.

3:00 AM is my genesis drop on Sound; a piece of music with a mesmerizing combination of synths and beats with a minimalistic, yet deeply resonating introduction that pays homage to House and EDM.
 
This track has been written, recorded, and produced by myself.
I hope you enjoy it as much as I enjoy creating it!
